<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu yī jiàn shì wǒ xīn lǐ zhī dào, jiù shì yé sū dào shì shàng bǎ wǒ lái xún zhǎo.
 yǒu yī jiàn shì wǒ xīn lǐ zhī dào, shì shén tīng le wài pó de dǎo gào.
 hé shuǐ qīng qīng liú, chuán ér yáo a yáo, wǒ yào fú shì zhǔ yé sū dào tiān yá hé hǎi jiǎo.
 ràng shì rén dōu zhī dào dōu tīng dào, yé sū ài wǒ dào shì shàng lái bǎ wǒ xún zhǎo.</lyrics>
